                    </div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="emoji">
                            <b>
                                &#128143
                            </b>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="subheading">
                            Organise to your liking
                        </h3>
                        <p class="paragraph">
                            Tag photos so you can revist a collection of photos easily! [Basketball] [ChineseFood] [Scenery] 
