                    </div>
                    <div class="steps">
                        <div class="emoji">
                            <b>
                                &#128126
                            </b>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="subheading">
                            Keep them private, or share with others
                        </h3>
                        <p class="paragraph">
                            Not all photos need be shared with the world. Keep moments personal that defines you.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-1">
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
